➜不要随便阻止你的宠物吃屎，那可能是件好事
http://www.sohu.com/a/413904680_624188	32432
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200819/a7c4ab8bb12648508a6bb0aaa1f6dc03.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知不觉就<strong>立秋</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着一整个夏天都没能减下的小肚子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是否暗自抱怨上天不公</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为什么人类想拥有肌肉需要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/20f5ca7f36974e7b98e5ac83fd65da00.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200819/5d6b9f5bcd88442d9bacaa6af23f34a2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">而别的动物想拥有肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只需要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/97de809897ea4ac291aae5cd0391c015.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讲真</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食肉动物好歹要搞点<strong>猎杀行动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有肌肉也算正常</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200819/6609c8ea82534fc893af0d5853f946de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你们这些吃素的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎么也长成了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200819/1396f75422234ff3ba9166727840b0ed.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/d6c3185662ae4a78aaa68f316a1943d0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至是这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200819/a2508550e20048a4aa9960df82adf8ed.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说好的长肌肉就得先补充<strong>蛋白质</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而蛋白质通常靠肉、蛋、奶来补充</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些吃素的动物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">究竟是怎么吃出一身腱子肉的？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/f6e53f25063542d1bfaa5d5ed6f8de66.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为人类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你日常想获取肉蛋奶非常简单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟那些觉得难的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经在进化途中被取代了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/6e61a3586bbc49cea5e7583a5567e6e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为普通动物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了刚出生那几年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有老妈的免费奶喝以外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想搞到其他的玩意儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么靠<strong>技巧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么靠<strong>蛮力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200819/7239a77f0a184c569704471afb0fa28b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连老虎狮子这种强悍野兽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也经常过着有上顿没下顿的生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为战五渣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然不能和它们争</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要想不被时代淘汰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就得谋求<strong>新的吃路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/a900817a15ea4cfc89c9e9f4123dbc6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这种食物还得有点讲究</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅得要<strong>容易获取</strong>还得<strong>数量多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能有效避免战五渣们菜鸡互啄争食物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很显然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在大自然中能满足这样条件的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无非就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/277e71913d284ac8b0faf9a6a8e10cad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下虽然是不会饿死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但极有可能成别人的盘中餐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以为了活下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们选择了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>变大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也就是为什么在陆地上长得大的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">通常都是吃素的原因之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/dd5cab3d9b4d4cd4bd47e39e3284d3ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说起大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就不得不提一种<strong>特别的动物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃进去的东西全拿去补身子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脑子是一点儿营养都没分到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">智商低到不知逃跑为何物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但凡见谁不爽都选择直接冲的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>犀牛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200819/3ab0e3aa60c14330b7d3ef4491535404.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一旦打起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算快被揍死</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">犀牛也<strong>绝对不会退缩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒不是犀牛对自己实力多有信心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是单纯的智商低到没恐惧这概念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以凡是有点智商的都不会跟它斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟这货又莽又大皮又厚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打起来得不偿失</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就使得它在自然界除了人类外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">基本没有天敌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/f3c010331ebb44b0a8c170e097d54f7b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且这些素食动物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大就算了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还浑身都是肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连吃了睡睡了吃的<strong>猪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平均体脂肪率也就18.2%左右</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而普通成年人的体脂率</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女性20%～25%</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男性15%～18%</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200819/9c8d90fa3f284fe1b3804414ebae2370.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于为什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就得从他们的<strong>消化系统</strong>说起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如<strong>反刍动物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拥有非常强大的<strong>胃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿<strong>牛</strong>来举例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它就有着四个非常美味强大的胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/abba7cdfd67840d7ac777e831ae4c543.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当牛在进食的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">内心想的只有一件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200819/3bd115506f344b54b812b7aa000ffa2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以它们通常不会细嚼慢咽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只会一股脑的先塞为敬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大部分都没好好嚼过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接进入瘤胃（毛肚）里囤着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等夜深人静思考牛生的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再反刍出来细细品味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而反刍通常<strong>不止一次</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟黑夜那么长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛小小的脑袋也有很多的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/7c8e4e90bce3486a818a2ad4e7f66882.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在反反复复地反刍后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食物会来到网胃（金钱肚）进行过筛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">筛后来到重瓣胃（牛百叶）烘干研磨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后进入皱胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结束一次完整的进食</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200819/6e8f43ec04d4403f92ec1a12a58d689f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这看似吃草的过程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实是个熬汤的过程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瘤胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是毛肚那里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">占了胃容积的80%</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">聚集了大量的微生物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们的使命就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">工作——繁殖——被吸收</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微生物自带<strong>特殊酶工具</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将植物内的纤维素逐级分解成葡萄糖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再经过发酵产生<strong>挥发性脂肪酸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一部分会被牛身体吸收利用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而另一部分像<strong>甲烷、二氧化碳</strong>等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就会被<strong>排出体外</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就是为什么会说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">温室效应跟牛有关系的原因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/14979c92bbdd4f6eadd4988320339d49.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在分解工作中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微生物也会获得一些糖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来合成<strong>自身糖原</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">储存在体内把自己养肥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微生物在将摄入的蛋白质</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分解成氨基酸的同时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也会利用一部分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来合成转变为<strong>自身蛋白质</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来壮大繁殖自家人口数量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛的胃其实可以算是一锅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>微生物浓汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200819/42eaf599c4394c408286ff697c973b2c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这锅浓汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅能帮助牛<strong>分解营养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也会被牛大量吸收</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你看牛似乎是在吃草</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实际人家在摄入材料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>熬高蛋白浓汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛那嘴基本就没停过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每天不停地咀嚼然后反刍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">煲出了不知道多少微生物浓汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再一锅接一锅地灌下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它不长肌肉谁长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/5802a15b22d14f28b2f13be0df5a3c98.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要说牛这能力有多强呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那大概就是基因突变一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缺点肌肉生长抑制素</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去抑制一下蓬勃的肌肉生长欲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们就能靠吃草长成这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/e86b887c6ad443e9b285bfc6449f3866.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了胃强大外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食草动物们的<strong>肠子</strong>也不是盖的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是真的长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如说兔子的肠道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能达到自身体长的20倍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凹凸的表面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅增加了食物和肠道的接触面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也减缓了食物的流速</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以便更大程度的吸收营养</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">使得兔子肉更加紧实美味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/8cf45ef831c3469982135a862c85a926.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且兔子虽然只有一个胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但它的<strong>盲肠</strong>能发酵产出一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光滑湿润富含蛋白质的<strong>便便球</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">兔子再次吃下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">便可以达到增肌的效果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以看到兔子吃屎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不要急着阻止</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">指不定是个好屎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200819/de3f7afa34fc4bd39f8e91ed020337f5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而以上技能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食肉动物们是没有的了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">特别是人类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进化中选择更大的<strong>脑子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说只占体重2%</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">耗能却占了20%</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果人类还像动物那样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天生就能拥有发达的肌肉的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就得和它们一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃了睡睡了吃才能补充能量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而那样操作你还想进化？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200819/f604d22ad69f41508a6977108a3b8a60.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以为了脑子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人体只能分泌<strong>肌肉生长抑制素</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来抑制肌肉的生长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以你想要练出大块大块的肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就得和天生基因对抗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200819/e03c96e5db1d4b94b39ece425667fcbb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算你靠努力对抗成功基因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有了肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要你咸鱼一段日子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肌肉又会缩水变软了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过也不是没有例外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在德国有个孩子出生天生自带肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传闻<strong>四岁半</strong>时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能双臂各举一个3公斤的哑铃了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过这全靠基因突变</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">减少了肌肉生长抑制素的合成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才有的这个效果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200819/42a426d6457f4adb8d31e936d81e3d67.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为普通人的你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅没有牛的胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更没有突变的基因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃再多的草</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也只是被拉出来的命</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以看完这篇文</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">安安心心吃肉去吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟你瘦了也不一定会有对象</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但吃肉一定是香的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/91e67d379d8e4930a35236082e218678.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>